net.floodlightcontroller.core

类 ControllerId

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.floodlightcontroller.core.ControllerId

  • public class ControllerId
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a unique id of this controller node. It is derived from the node id as returned by ISyncService.getLocalNodeId().

    Note that the unconfigured Node Id is not supported. Users are encouraged to represent an unconfigured Controller Node by Optional.absent().
